column4: ^statusCode:{"200":"The topic.","400":"Indicates a bad request error. It could be caused by an unexpected request body format or other forms of request validation failure.","401":"Indicates a client authentication error. Kafka authentication failures will contain error code 40101 in the response body.","403":"Indicates a client authorization error. Kafka authorization failures will contain error code 40301 in the response body.","429":"Indicates that a rate limit threshold has been reached, and the client should retry again later.","5XX":"A server-side problem that might not be addressable from the client side. Retriable Kafka errors will contain error code 50003 in the response body."}
